title: Ireland fails to qualify for grand final of Eurovision Song Contest
description: Ireland has failed to qualify for the grand final of the Eurovision Song Contest, despite the best efforts of Wild Youth.

title: Britain would 'welcome' intervention by China to bring peace in Ukraine, says James Cleverly
description: The foreign secretary has said he would "welcome" any intervention by China that could help bring the war between Russia and Ukraine to an end.

title: Explosions sound over Kyiv as Russia marks Victory Day - but nightly strikes fail to break Ukraine's resolve
description: As dawn broke, just hours before Russia's Victory Day parade, explosions sounded over the Ukrainian capital.

title: This was not a normal Victory Day - so many have bought into the Kremlin's narrative
description: Victory Day parades in Russia generally see throngs of people lining the city's main thoroughfares, cheering on the tanks as they pass, the armoured vehicles and S-400 anti-aircraft systems and, the spectator's favourite, the fearsome YARS intercontinental ballistic missile capable of delivering a world-ending nuclear payload across the globe.

title: Putin's 'grotesque fictions' exposed on much-changed Victory Day
description: It has been said the only glue that holds Russia together is the memory of its great victory over Nazi Germany.

title: Man kept father's dead body in freezer 'so he could talk to him'
description: A man has been caught storing his dead father's body in his freezer.

title: Pakistan's former prime minister Imran Khan detained in Islamabad
description: Imran Khan, the former prime minister of Pakistan, has been detained, local media has reported.

title: How does Russia's scaled-back Victory Day parade compare to previous years?
description: Soldiers marching through the streets of Moscow, armoured vehicles rolling across Red Square and a rallying cry from Vladimir Putin talking of the West's "real war".

title: Thousands of women could be saved every year thanks to new way of treating bleeding
description: A new method of treating women suffering severe bleeding after childbirth  reduces the number of maternal deaths by 60%, researchers have found.

title: Just one tank rolls through Moscow's Red Square for stripped back Victory Day parade
description: Just one tank rolled through Moscow and no aircraft soared overhead as Vladimir Putin spoke at a stripped-down Victory Day parade in Red Square.

title: Israel kills three Islamic Jihad commanders in targeted Gaza strikes
description: Israel has bombed the Gaza Strip overnight, killing three senior commanders of the Palestinian Islamic Jihad group.
